<title>Web Hosting Terms of Service @ TDG Network</title>
<span style='font-family:Arial'><br>
Web Hosting Terms of Service<o:p></o:p></span></h1>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;text-align:justify;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;
color:#00007F'>1.) Account Creation </span><span style='font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;text-align:justify;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;
color:#00007F'>Once we receive your payment and screen your order, to remove
fraudulent users, we will create your account.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>The customer is responsible for providing an email address, independent of
the one we will be providing (i.e. NOT <span class=GramE>the @</span> the
domain(s) you are signing up for). </span><span style='font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;text-align:justify;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;
color:#00007F'><br>
2.) Content </span><span style='font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;text-align:justify;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;
color:#00007F'>TDG Web Hosting Service (hereinafter ‘TDGWHS’) will only be used
for lawful purposes.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>We will not
support, among other things at our sole discretion: copyrighted materials,
material we judge to be threatening or obscene, indecent material or
pornography.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>The customer agrees to
indemnify and hold harmless TDGWHS from any claims resulting from the use of
our services, unless it stems from <span class=SpellE>TDGWHS’s</span> gross
negligence.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>All grievances must be
provided, in writing, to TDGWHS with at least 30 days notice. <a
href="mailto:webhosting@thedruidsgrove.org">webhosting@thedruidsgrove.org</a></span><span
style='font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:13.5pt;text-align:justify;mso-pagination:none;mso-layout-grid-align:
none;text-autospace:none'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial;
color:#00007F'>Examples of unacceptable material:</span><span style='font-family:
Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:49.5pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-pagination:
none;tab-stops:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>·<span style='mso-tab-count:1'> </span><span
