color:#00007F'><br>
3.) Zero-Tolerance Spam Policy </span><span style='font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:49.5pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-pagination:
none;tab-stops:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>·<span style='mso-tab-count:1'> </span><span
style='color:#00007F'>TDGWHS takes a zero-tolerance stance against sending of
unsolicited e-mail, bulk emailing, and spam. &quot;Safe lists&quot; and
&quot;double opt-in&quot; will be treated as spam.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Any customer caught sending out spam, will
have their account terminated and at our earliest convenience. No refunds will
be honored.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:49.5pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-pagination:
none;tab-stops:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>·<span style='mso-tab-count:1'> </span><span
style='color:#00007F'>TDG</span><span style='color:black'>WHS</span><span
style='color:#00007F'> reserves the right to require changes or disable as
necessary any website, account, database, or other component that does not comply
with our anti-spam policy, at its sole discretion.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>TDGWHS also reserves the right to make any
such modifications, as required, should an emergency arise. Emergency is
classified as anything that violates the contract such as Pornography, Memory
Hogging Programs, running of hotmail type service, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:30.0pt;margin-bottom:
5.0pt;margin-left:49.5pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-pagination:
none;tab-stops:.5in;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Arial'>·<span style='mso-tab-count:1'> </span><span
style='color:#00007F'>TDGWHS reserves the right to charge the customer a clean
up fee, for any unsolicited e-mails sent through our service. This includes but
is not limited to removal copyrighted materials, material we judge to be
threatening or obscene, indecent material or pornography.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>The cost of the clean up fee is left
entirely to the discretion of TDGWHS. Cost of a clean up fee can run as high as
